      <title>日产股价上涨令亚洲做空最多的汽车制造商交易员蒙受损失</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/nissan-share-rally-burns-traders-in-asia-s-most-shorted-carmaker</link>
      <description><![CDATA[对于做空日产汽车公司（亚洲做空量最大的汽车制造商）的交易员来说，这是痛苦的一周，因为在与实力更强大的竞争对手本田汽车公司进行合并谈判后，日产汽车公司的股价在两天内飙升了 30％ 以上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/nissan-share-rally-burns-traders-in-asia-s-most-shorted-carmaker</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 05:10:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>汽车制造商应对消费放缓，欧洲汽车销量下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/europe-car-sales-dip-as-automakers-battle-consumer-slowdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于需求放缓，欧洲汽车销量上个月出现下滑，该地区最大的汽车制造商正努力应对引发行业危机的问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/europe-car-sales-dip-as-automakers-battle-consumer-slowdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲医疗保健股将迎来受美国政治影响的一年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/european-health-stocks-brace-for-a-year-clouded-by-us-politics</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲医疗保健股在 2024 年最后几个月跌至历史低位后，在新的一年里面临着美国政治和新药高风险试验结果的威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/european-health-stocks-brace-for-a-year-clouded-by-us-politics</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>嘉能可增加新加坡布科姆工厂的中东石油采购量</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/glencore-boosts-middle-east-oil-buying-for-singapore-bukom-plant</link>
      <description><![CDATA[交易商称，嘉能可公司 (Glencore Plc) 本月已成为中东现货石油的活跃买家，该公司开始为新加坡的布科姆 (Bukom) 炼油厂采购原油。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/glencore-boosts-middle-east-oil-buying-for-singapore-bukom-plant</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 04:45:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲交易员预计 2025 年将有更多 IPO 和可转换债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/asia-dealmakers-see-more-ipos-convertible-bonds-in-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中国交易保持低迷，亚洲首次公开募股 (IPO) 所占比例已降至八年来的最低水平，投资银行家们希望 2025 年亚洲首次公开募股 (IPO) 能在其股权资本市场中占据更大份额。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/asia-dealmakers-see-more-ipos-convertible-bonds-in-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 04:39:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中石化：2025 年起中国汽油需求将快速下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/china-s-gasoline-demand-to-fall-quickly-from-2025-sinopec-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国最大的炼油商表示，该国的汽油需求去年已达到峰值，随着电动汽车普及步伐加快，汽油需求将加速下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/china-s-gasoline-demand-to-fall-quickly-from-2025-sinopec-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 04:19:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>策略师称，由于日本央行不加息，日元前景恶化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/yen-s-outlook-worsens-as-boj-skips-rate-hike-strategists-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[策略师们表示，日本央行放弃可能的加息后，日元的前景正在恶化，而央行的经济声明可以看作是有些鸽派。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/yen-s-outlook-worsens-as-boj-skips-rate-hike-strategists-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 04:09:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储降息后华尔街交易员纷纷退出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/wall-street-traders-rush-for-the-exit-after-fed-s-rate-cut-shift</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在引发金融市场大幅上涨近一年后，美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔周三却做出了完全相反的举动，对 2025 年的降息持谨慎态度，令投资者感到震惊。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/wall-street-traders-rush-for-the-exit-after-fed-s-rate-cut-shift</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 00:40:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲股市回落；日元下跌，日本央行按兵不动：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储预测明年降息次数减少，亚洲股市周四下跌。日本央行未提高借贷成本，日元下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 22:59:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沙特全球港口寻求银行帮助，筹资额高达 10 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/saudi-port-operator-said-to-pick-banks-for-up-to-1-billion-ipo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，沙特全球港口公司 (Saudi Global Ports Co.) 已选定高盛集团 (Goldman Sachs Group Inc.) 和汇丰控股有限公司 (HSBC Holdings Plc) 等银行协助安排利雅得计划中的首次公开募股 (IPO)。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/saudi-port-operator-said-to-pick-banks-for-up-to-1-billion-ipo</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 12:44:08 GMT</pubDate>
